What we do for food businesses

Logo & Brand Kit

3 concepts, 2 rounds of revisions, final files (SVG/PNG/PDF), colour & type choices, icon set, social avatars.

Instagram Handling

Content calendar, daily story templates, 12–20 posts/mo, captions/hashtags, geo‑tags, scheduling & comments.

Menu, Flyers & Posters

Dine‑in menus, QR menus, table tents, promos, grand‑opening & seasonal campaign creatives (print & digital).

Add‑ons: short video reels, photo shoot coordination, Google Business profile refresh, basic landing pages.

Simple process

1. 30‑min chat

Goals, audience, signature dishes, vibe. Quick audit of your current socials.

2. Look & calendar

Logo/menu directions + a 4‑week content plan. You approve & we start.

3. Launch & iterate

We design, post and report. What brings bookings stays; the rest we tweak.
